# macOS (ld64) exported-symbols allowlist for libhaze.dylib — the analogue of
# linker/haze_exports.map. Everything not matched here is made local, so the
# absorbed OpenFHE/libnbfhetch/bridge symbols stay private and cannot collide
# with another OpenFHE in the same process. Mach-O prefixes C symbols with an
# underscore, so haze's `extern "C" haze*` C ABI is `_haze*`.
_haze*
